    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>Network card</entry>
    <entry>Yes</entry>
    <entry>Emulates an NE2000 compatible network card (ISA / PCI) or an Intel(R)
    82540EM Gigabit Ethernet adapter (PCI). On Windows NT/2000, Linux, FreeBSD,
