    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>USB</entry>
    <entry>Yes</entry>
    <entry>Four types of host controllers (UHCI, OHCI, EHCI and xHCI) and the
    devices 'mouse', 'tablet', 'keypad', 'disk', 'cdrom', 'floppy, ''hub' and
